blogPost.excerpt: The US president stumbled while boarding Air Force One on his way to visit to Atlanta, Georgia, to meet with Asian American community leaders. Biden tripped on the steps up to the plane, before recovering and carrying on unaided, turning to salute at the top. The 78-year-old fractured his right foot in November 2020 while playing with his dog Major
blogPost.body: The US president stumbled while boarding Air Force One on his way to visit to Atlanta, Georgia, to meet with Asian American community leaders. Biden tripped on the steps up to the plane, before recovering and carrying on unaided, turning to salute at the top. The 78-year-old fractured his right foot in November 2020 while playing with his dog Major
blogPost.title: Joe Biden stumbles on steps of Air Force One

localize.title: 乔-拜登在空军一号的台阶上摔了一跤
localize.description: 美国总统在前往佐治亚州亚特兰大市访问，与亚裔美国人社区领袖会面的途中，登上空军一号时跌倒。拜登在上飞机的台阶上被绊倒，随后恢复过来，没有人搀扶，转身在机顶敬礼。这位78岁的老人在2020年11月与爱犬Major玩耍时右脚骨折。

localize.title: 喬-拜登在空軍一號的臺階上摔了一跤
localize.description: 美國總統在前往佐治亞州亞特蘭大市訪問，與亞裔美國人社區領袖會面的途中，登上空軍一號時跌倒。拜登在上飛機的臺階上被絆倒，隨後恢復過來，沒有人攙扶，轉身在機頂敬禮。這位78歲的老人在2020年11月與愛犬Major玩耍時右腳骨折。
